            "type": "markdown",
            "markdown": "# Davis CoPilot\n### DQL is super powerful, but what if we could use generative AI to do some of the hard work for us? Let's use **[Davis CoPilot](https://docs.dynatrace.com/docs/discover-dynatrace/platform/davis-ai/copilot/copilot-getting-started)** to build the DQL for some common use cases\n![](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dynatrace-wwse/workshop-dynatrace-log-analytics/refs/heads/main/assets/images/logs-copilot_davis_ai_marketecture.png)"
        },
        {
            "id": "dfda42c9-5445-430d-87e6-4d66273d5722",
            "type": "markdown",
            "markdown": "**Get a high level overview of your logs**\n\n```Summarize all logs by log level```"
        },
        {
            "id": "dbff690e-6c6f-45b7-9e9f-102f6d3ea9e1",
            "type": "dql",
            "filterSegments": [],
            "drilldownPath": [],
            "previousFilterSegments": [],
            "subType": "davis-copilot",
            "davisCopilot": {
                "prompt": "",
                "response": {
                    "status": "idle"
                },
                "showDqlSnippet": false,
                "feedbackProvided": false
            },
            "state": {
                "input": {
                    "timeframe": {
                        "from": "now()-2h",
                        "to": "now()"
                    },
                    "value": ""
                },
                "visualizationSettings": {
                    "autoSelectVisualization": true,
                    "chartSettings": {}
                },
                "querySettings": {
                    "maxResultRecords": 1000,
                    "defaultScanLimitGbytes": 500,
                    "maxResultMegaBytes": 1,
                    "defaultSamplingRatio": 10,
                    "enableSampling": false
                },
                "state": "idle",
                "davis": {
                    "includeLogs": true,
                    "davisVisualization": {
                        "isAvailable": true
                    }
                }
            }
        },
